[recto] Tower of Babel. Witt Library. L. van Valckenborch. 7 Towers of Babel as Valckenborch, among these one in Munich, Pinakothek nearest to Bruegel clearly based on Bruegel's Van Beuningen version; Ad Tower of Babel generally: 1) The Vienna picture is Nimrod's visit to the town; 2) The Van Beuningen picture is the building of the tower; [verso] more Towers of Babel under Maerten van Valckenborch.
